      "type": "nine15--ctas",
      "settings": {
        "title": "Go ahead, reach out, and make a connection. It feels good.",
        "text": "<p>“Hello” is one of those rare words that can mean a lot of things… it can be a question, an expression, or a greeting. No matter the nuance, it’s always a connection of some sort. We love Hello?! for that reason, and we were inspired by the connection Consuela creates among people in making our Spring 2025 collection.</p>",
