    "7248c945-b232-4592-8db9-c4cfa37998ae": {
      "type": "nine15--ctas",
      "settings": {
        "title": "You had me at Hello.",
        "text": "<p> This collection boasts some of our favorite elements: the brightest, most vibrant pinks, yellows, and greens, shiny bronze embroidery, crystal-studded sunsets, handcrafted bag charms, festive fruity and floral disco ball prints, and many woven textures and intricate handcrafted details. We even created a new floating floral embroidery pattern that is just the friendliest greeting.  And we’re introducing new silhouettes that put the FUN in functional.⁠</p>\n<p> \n<b>\n<i>\nA confident wave, a playful glance, a shared smile, or an impactful, everlasting conversation…every connection starts with a Hello!\n</b>\n</i>\n⁠</p>",
