        "text": "<p>Once the design and product teams have completed the collection, it's the visual and marketing teams' mission to tell the story. What set the creative journey in motion was discovering Rancho Pillow, a unique compound near the tiny art town of Round Top, Texas. With its poetic and playful vibe, colorful architecture, and collected curiosities, this location truly captured the essence of our brand and this new collection.</p>\n<p><B>We hope this collection inspires you to embark on your own adventure and find moments of serenity and wonder in your everyday life.</B></p>",
